A must-have school accessory, ideal for both artists and students with plenty of space to host your fluo highlighters and techpoint pens. A lovely simple case that safeguards your much-beloved stationery in its zippered compartment. 
Absolutely adorable, available in both plain colours and attractive patterns.

title: Eastpak provider hyper hippo
description: Grab-and-go! Featuring two main roomy compartments and a padded laptop sleeve for optimal security, the Eastpak Provider will become your most reliable mate. Especially designed to host all your gear and techy kits, this backpack provides super convenience thanks to its little extras that will help you keep organized, such as the ultimate key keeper, a perfect accessory for energetic users! Make the most out of the Eastpak Provider, available in a wide variety of urban colours and patterns!

• Laptop sleeve 38 x 29 x 5cm
  • Two large compartments including padded laptop sleeve
  • Padded bottom
  • Front organizer pocket with detachable key keeper
  • Comfortable quilted padded back
  • Thick padded shoulder straps with SGS
  • Side compression straps
  • Rubber molded handle
